text: KF Përparimi (, FK Perparimi) is a football club based in the village of Rečane near Gostivar, North Macedonia. They recently competed in the Macedonian Third League (West Division). ==History== The club was founded in 1974. ==References== ==External links== *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Football Federation of Macedonia Perparimi Category:Association football clubs established in 1974 Category:1974 establishments in the Socialist Republic of Macedonia FK Perparimi
